org.sql: SELECT current_relations.* FROM current_relations INNER JOIN current_relation_members ON current_relation_members.relation_id = current_relations.id WHERE current_relation_members.member_type = "$1" AND current_relation_members.member_id IN ("$2", "$3") AND current_relations.visible = "$4"
